author: Rose Lilah
title: 6LACK & Jhene Aiko - First F*ck
text:
100% (3) Listen to a new collaboration from buzzing artist 6lack and Jhene Aiko. 
6lack continues the come-up. The Atlanta singer-sometimes-rapper has been buzzing heavily since his last release, Free 6lac k, and the upwards trend is only continuing with his latest collaboration, a duet alongside Jhene Aiko . This isn't even the biggest co-sign he's received as a singer, The Weeknd has already given 6lack his seal of approval, enlisting him for the North American leg of his Starboy tour, as well as bringing him out for a surprise performance in LA. Despite being from ATL, he definitely has a TO-approved sound. 
The joint record, "First F*ck," is the perfect bedroom jam, with a slow-moving beat that finds 6lack drawling about spending a night with a ladyfriend, before Jhene chimes in with her perspective. Take a listen. 
We'll keep you posted if more information on the collaboration arrives. First F*ck
